    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> in <strong>cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>until evenly flattened</p><p>Add the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> to a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong>, the <strong>remaining chicken stock mix</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the chicken is fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
