    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>sliced ciabatta</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 5 min or until warmed through</p>",
